<br>
1.  Will the gnome Watchmen (or any other mob) join in the fight against Renux?  We all know how much it sucks to be KSed by a guard.<br>
<br>
2.  Can anyone recommend a good kiting circuit in Steamfont?  In my experience, rage-kiting is most effective over flat ground without too many obstacles, with room for gentle turns.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uteramenor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Teramenor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/29/01 1:26:35 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Renux and Gnomish Law</span><hr size=1> 1. No idea. We didn't go anywhere near any other mobs while fighting Renux, especially not guards. Didn't want to risk it.<br>
<br>
2. We basically kited Renux around in a circle some ways east of Ak'anon, pretty much south/southwest from the windmills, at around (-1000, -500). There's a big ditch there, and to the east is a sizable flat area. Frankly, as long as Renux is snared, you don't need a very big area at all to keep her occupied. Just make sure your snarer chain-snares her so that he keeps aggro, and the meleers don't pull aggro. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uteramenor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Teramenor</A> at: 11/29/01 1:27:35 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utirrentherogue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tirren the Rogue</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/29/01 2:09:51 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Renux and Gnomish Law</span><hr size=1> From my experience in killing Renux:<br>
<br>
Had 60 warrior, 60 rogue, 54 rogue &lt;me&gt;,  52 Rogue, 60 Ranger, 60 druid.<br>
<br>
Ranger attempted the pull after Renux was spawned but got the beatdown &lt;doh!&gt;. Luckily, the 52 Rogue who had turned the items in picked Renux up and kited her in circles while we waited for the 60 druid to port in and the 60 ranger to get rezzed back. Then, the druid took over the kite, snared Renux, and pulled safely to Lfay zone.<br>
<br>
As long as Renux is aggroed, she will not despawn. Therefore, when kiting, keep her close! Once she was at Lfay zone, the druid kited her around in a tight circle, casting snare again and again to keep aggro. After a minute or so of backstabbing, slashing, and bashing, Renux died.<br>
<br>
So basically, kite in a circle, and keep the snarer with aggro, and you should be fine. Melees and a druid are all you need; she goes down fast! Also, unsure bout the watchmen aggro, sorry for that <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Tirren Piesnatcher<br>
54 Halfling Rogue<br>
Xev <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/upatofnaud.showPublicProfile?language=EN>patofnaud</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/29/01 2:19:51 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Renux and Gnomish Law</span><hr size=1> The Watchmen will aggro and try to kill any members of you party who are KoS to gnomes.<br>
<br>
The Watchman may be on the same faction as Yelnar but not Renux, so I can't see why they would join in. But I would never risk it. One AE, one miss placed arrow, and it will get nasty. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utannblackpoint.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tann Blackpoint</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/29/01 4:55:12 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Renux and Gnomish Law</span><hr size=1> Never had any problems with othe mobs assisting unless you are kos to that mob.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13>Quests of Norrath</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
